{"word":"κεντρόω","slug":"κεντρόω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κεντρόω</b></el> <el>(κεντρόω,) ( φυτ. <el>-ώσω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:κέντρον'><el>κέντρον</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to furnish with a sting:—</i> <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be so furnished, to sting</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to strike with a goad</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}